  09 Aug 2015; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org>
  +files/postinstall-1.18-en.txt, +files/postupgrade-1.16-en.txt,
  +mediawiki-1.19.23.ebuild, +mediawiki-1.19.24.ebuild,
